    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1924-06-21T13:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1924-06-21T13:00:00-05:00" n="326"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d326">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">494.11 L 25/16: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Ambassador in Japan</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Woods</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-06-21T14:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">June 21, 1924—2 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>105. Embassy’s number 60, April 1st, 2 p.m. You are authorized to accept $15,000
                    United States currency offered by Foreign Office in settlement of Langdon claim.
                    Endeavor effect prompt settlement. Telegraph when payment made.<note n="80"
                        xml:id="d326fn80">The Chargé in Japan reported on July 5, 1924, that he had
                        been handed on that date, by the Foreign Office, a draft for $15,000 United
                        States currency in settlement of the Langdon claim (file no. 494.11 L
                        25/18).</note>
                </p>
                <p>You may explain to Foreign Office that offer is accepted because of willingness
                    of parents of Langdon that matter be settled in that manner.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
